---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for China Buyer Prep."
  canonical="/privacy/"
>
  <section class="content-page">
    <header class="page-header">
      <span class="eyebrow">Legal</span>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p>China Buyer Prep is a practical guide website. This page explains how we handle basic visitor information.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="prose">
      <h2>Information we collect</h2>
      <p>We may collect basic analytics information such as pages visited, referring pages, browser type, device type, and approximate region. If you contact us directly, we may receive the information you choose to send.</p>

      <h2>How we use information</h2>
      <p>We use this information to improve site content, maintain site security, understand which guides are useful, and respond to messages.</p>

      <h2>Third-party services</h2>
      <p>The site may use hosting, analytics, search, or performance tools that process limited technical information. These services operate under their own privacy terms.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>If you have a privacy question, contact us through the <a href="/contact/">contact page</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
